ITEM.name = "M84 Stun Grenade"
ITEM.description = "The M84 Stun Grenade, a non-lethal explosive device, is designed to temporarily incapacitate targets through a blinding flash of light and a deafeningly loud blast. Primarily used in military and law enforcement operations, the M84 is known for its swift and disorienting effects, rendering adversaries disoriented and vulnerable. Upon detonation, it emits a bright, intense light and a powerful concussive shockwave, causing sensory overload and disrupting the target's cognitive functions. The grenade's casing is constructed from durable materials to withstand rough handling and ensure reliable deployment in various combat scenarios. With its ability to neutralize threats without causing permanent harm, the M84 Stun Grenade remains an essential tool for tactical engagements where minimizing casualties is of utmost importance."
